WEBVTT

00:01.607 --> 00:03.183
You are being watched.

00:04.111 --> 00:06.142
The government has
a secret system.

00:06.434 --> 00:10.048
A machine that spies on
you every hour of every day.

00:10.789 --> 00:12.922
I know because I built it.

00:13.385 --> 00:15.714
I designed the machine to
detect acts of terror, but,

00:15.799 --> 00:17.286
it sees everything.

00:17.435 --> 00:20.010
Violent crimes involving
ordinary people.

00:20.217 --> 00:21.445
People like you.

00:21.568 --> 00:24.040
Crimes that the government
considered irrelevant.

00:25.003 --> 00:28.122
They wouldn't act,
so I decided I would.

00:28.124 --> 00:30.641
But I needed a partner.

00:30.643 --> 00:32.643
Someone with the skills to intervene.

00:32.645 --> 00:35.463
Hunted by the authorities,

00:35.465 --> 00:37.198
we work in secret.

00:37.200 --> 00:39.150
You'll never find us.

00:39.152 --> 00:41.185
But victim or perpetrator,

00:41.187 --> 00:42.653
if your number's up,

00:42.655 --> 00:44.021
we'll find you.

00:45.375 --> 00:49.130
